+
+license_key    = "your-license-key"
+license_secret = "your-license-secret"
+
+tags = ["ztna", "production", "2-nic"]
+```
+
+### Example 4: Using Remote OVA URL
+
+```hcl
+# terraform.tfvars
+number_of_nics = "1"
+
+datacenter = "Production-DC"
+datastore  = "datastore1"
+
